        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span>&nbsp;Interact</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Your mind becomes clear and cognition flows freely, but physical matters seem ephemeral.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong> You gain a +3 item bonus to Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, and Society checks and all checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge}. Your critical failures on @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} checks become failures instead. You become trained in one Intelligence-based skill [Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, Society], chosen at creation.</p>\n<p><strong>Drawback</strong>&nbsp;You take a -2 penalty to weapon and unarmed attack rolls, Athletics checks, and acrobatics checks. You can carry 2 less Bulk than normal before becoming encumbered, and the maximum Bulk you can carry is reduced by 4.</p>\n<p><strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 hour.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.qit1mLbJUyRTYcPU]{Effect: Cognitive Mutagen (Greater)}</p>",
